#Task6:

#collect one string from user:

#string: computer
#output: c6r

#string: mathematics
#output: m9s

#Program
str1=input("Define the str1: ")
                 
output_str = str1[0] + str(len(str1)-2) + str(str1[len(str1)-1])

print(output_str)

#output
Define the str1: computer
c6r
Define the str1: mathematics
m9s
